    "body": "Is there a recommend approach for when a package changes build system? The package in question is `kahip` [1], which has changed from SCons (v.2) to CMake (v.3). The current Spack package is for KaHIP version 2.0 and uses SCons. The latest KaHIP release series is v.3.\r\n\r\n[1] https://github.com/spack/spack/blob/e5bbb6e5b4a1af25dd46101bfc044d04deb10cb5/var/spack/repos/builtin/packages/kahip/package.py",
